salt-grain.name: ShadowEvaporationTool
salt-grain.title: Shadow Evaporation Tool
salt-grain.doc: Graphical tool that facilitates the mask design and process creation for the shadow (angular) evaporation technique. The process parameters (mask height, deposition angles) can be specified and the resulting structures are automatically generated as new GDS layers.
